 different functions and locations over my career of 22 years. At Voltas, we engender an environment of constant development. This allows me to hone my skills by accepting and accomplishing new assignments, shouldering additional cross-functional responsibilities, deputations for business growth and going beyond the operational activities to make a difference to the organisation. UPBG's dynamics have made me believe in carrying out a sustainable business in an innovative way.

