I was given the opportunity to participate in the Junior management leadership development program organized by Voltas limited. The course was conducted at a reputed management institute in Pune called NICMAR (National Institute of Construction management & research). I was also nominated for learning programmes hosted on the Voltas Virtual Campus. These ranged from Digital, Technology, compliance, Project Management, Leadership, Sales to Marketing, professional development.

</p><p class="testimonial-name">Satish Labade</p><p class="testimonial-designation">Sr. Project Engineer - Mechanical</p><i class="fa fa-times card-collapse-button" aria-hidden="true"></i></div></div></div></div></div>   {!-- ra:00000000731df2a90000000075fe1fc5 --}   {!-- bloqs:end:981 --}
